AddressInfo.Title: Bridge Street Inn
AddressInfo.AccessComments: EV station is powered by a Type 2 40amp charger.  Simply remove the cone in the EV parking space, pull in, flip the electric lever and connect.   The Bridge Street Inn is located within walking distances of restaurants, galleries, and shops.
